    "campaignDescription": "<p>Innovate UK, a department of UKRI and the UK's national innovation agency, is dedicated to fostering business-led innovation across all sectors and regions. Its mission is to support innovative enterprises from inception through scaling. This commitment is vividly articulated in their new prospectus, launched on 19 March 2026. A highlight video, featuring Executive Chair Tom Adeyoola, illustrates their vision to transform breakthrough ideas into UK industry giants, helping innovators establish, grow, and prosper within the nation. Explore their comprehensive strategy in the full prospectus to understand how Innovate UK is shaping the future of innovation.</p>",
